SELECT 
date(roma_dt_registro)    AS DT_REGISTRO_AGRUP
,roma_dt_situacao         AS DATA_SITUACAO
,pedv.pedv_dt_registro    AS DATA_REGISTRO   
,roma_id_agrurom          AS AGRUPAMENTO
,roma_id_programa         AS PROGRAMA		
,roma_id_onda             AS ONDA
,pedv_id_prevol           AS PREVOLUME
,roma_id_local_dest       AS ID_LOCAL_DESTINO
,pedv_documento_externo   AS ENTREGA	
,pedv_id_rota             AS LOJA  
,hllj_nome                AS LOJA_NOME
,loca_id_claloc           AS CLASSE	
,roma_id_local_orig       AS ID_LOCAL
,loca_descricao           AS ENDERECO
,roma_usuario             AS OPERADOR
,roma_id_rom              AS ID_ROMANEIO
,roma_pallet_cheio        AS PALETE_CHEIO
,roma_situacao            AS SITUACAO
,CASE
  WHEN agro_classificacao = 'SI' THEN 'SIMPLES'  
  WHEN agro_classificacao = 'CO' THEN 'COMPLEXO'
  ELSE 'SEM PARÃ‚METRO'  END       AS CLASSIFICACAO
,roma_tp_rom              AS TIPO_ROM
,romd_id_item             as ITEM
,item_cod_terceiro        as COD_TERCEIRO 
,i.item_nome              AS DESCRICAO 
,romd_qt                  AS QUANTIDADE
,romd_qt_atend            AS QUANTIDADE_ATENDIDA
,'EG' || agrup.agro_id_coleta     AS EG 


 FROM `b2w-bee-analytics.raw_wms_tables_current.wlasa_romaneio` roma

 LEFT JOIN `b2w-bee-analytics.raw_wms_tables_current.wlasa_romaneio_detalhe` romd
	on romd.romd_id_rom = roma.roma_id_rom
        and date(romd.process_time) <= current_date 

 LEFT JOIN `b2w-bee-analytics.raw_wms_tables_current.wlasa_agrupamento_romaneio` agrup
      on roma.roma_id_agrurom = agrup.agro_id_agrurom
      and date(agrup.process_time) <= current_date         

 LEFT JOIN  `b2w-bee-analytics.raw_wms_tables_current.wlasa_pedido_cab` pedv 
    ON  roma.roma_id_ped = pedv.pedv_id_ped
    and date(pedv.process_time) <= current_date       

 LEFT JOIN b2w-bee-analytics.raw_wms_tables_current.wlasa_item  AS i
        ON romd.romd_id_item  = i.item_id_item
        AND DATE(i.process_time) <= CURRENT_DATE        

  left join `b2w-bee-analytics.raw_wms_tables.wlasa_local` local
      on   local.loca_id_local  = roma.roma_id_local_orig  
      and date(local.process_time) <= current_date 
 
left join `b2w-bee-analytics.raw_wms_tables.wlasa_hora_limite_loja`  nome
      on hllj_cod_loja = pedv_id_rota
      and date(nome.process_time) <= current_date  

 
  WHERE DATE(roma.process_time)  <= CURRENT_DATE    
    AND roma_situacao <> 'LI'
    AND roma_situacao <> 'CA'
    AND pedv_id_warranty  = '101'
    AND roma_id_ressupri IS NULL 
    AND roma_tp_rom  <> 'A'
    and roma_id_planta = 'UBER'
